python-magnetcooling (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Thermal-hydraulic calculations for water-cooled high-field magnets.
  * Support for multiple heat transfer correlations.
  * IAPWS-IF97 water properties integration.
  * Friction models for turbulent flow.
  * Heat exchanger analysis capabilities.
  * Unit-aware calculations with pint.

